data.description: Have you been searching for a spacious house on a large lot in the Ozark School district?  This is it!  With 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and two living areas, this home has room for everyone!  Engineered hardwood floors span the main living room, kitchen and dining space. The kitchen boasts dark cabinets, granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances, including a smart refrigerator that stays with the house!  The dining area offers a big bay window which allows lots of natural light.  The main floor includes the master suite with large soaking tub, dual sink vanity, 2 closets, and separate shower. This split bedroom plan has 2 additional bedrooms (one with a vaulted ceiling!) and a second bathroom also on the main floor. The laundry room is centrally located for convenience.  Downstairs you'll find a large second living area as well as the fourth bedroom and third full bathroom. The single side of the three-car garage is extra deep providing storage room for a boat or even space for your home gym or crafting hobby!  This house offers a fully fenced backyard and sits at the end of a culd e sac on a .38 acre lot with no homes behind it giving you additional privacy!   Call today for a private tour.
